        {{#> case/rightColumn}}
            <h4>Review quantitative data</h4>
            <p>I worked closely with the Analyst in the team to review data from customer service,
                and interactions recorded in <a href="https://www.hotjar.com/">Hotjar</a>.
            </p>

            <h4>User testing</h4>

            <p>I conducted remote unmoderated user
                testing on <a href="https://www.usertesting.com/">Usertesting.com</a> to quickly dig deeper into why some issues occurred. The main takeaways were that:
            <p>
            <ul>
                <li>some buttons were hard to discover</li>
                <li>some content wasn't where users expected it to be.</li>
                <li>several section names sounded similar, which made it difficult to know what content to
                    expect in each section.
                </li>
                <li>the structure was too deep: after expanding a few subsections without finding what they
                    were looking for, users just gave up.
                </li>
            </ul>

            <h4>Workshop</h4>
            <p>A workshop was led by the Product Owner and Design Lead. I presented an overview of
            all the issues encountered on the Accommodation page.</p>
            <p>At the end of the workshop, we had a prioritised list of opportunities to act on. High up the list
            was re-organising the content on the page, and increasing affordance for key features.</p>
